Due to the PSG's previous sanctions, UEFA is following more closely than usual attempts to circumvent the rules.
Sources informed of the situation said Thursday that UEFA had not negotiated with PSG about Neymar's move.
Sources gave an interview to the Associated Press news agency on the condition that their identities are not disclosed because they have no authority to discuss the PSG's situation.
